#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "快速入门"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a new project"
msgstr "创建一个新项目"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Kdenlive directory structure</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kdenlive 目录结构</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Kdenlive directory structure</para>"
msgstr "<para>Kdenlive 目录结构</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first step is creating a new (empty) folder for our new project. I will "
"call it <filename>quickstart-tutorial/</filename> in this tutorial. Then get "
"some sample video clips, or download them from here:<ulink url=\"http://"
"granjow.net/uploads/kdenlive/manual/kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-avi.tar."
"bz2\">kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-avi.tar.bz2</ulink> (7 "
"MB)<footnote><para>If you prefer Theora (which you probably don’t since Ogg "
"Video usually causes problems), you can alternatively download <ulink url="
"\"http://granjow.net/uploads/kdenlive/manual/kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-"
"ogv.tar.bz2\">kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-ogv.tar.bz2</ulink>.</para></"
"footnote>, and extract them to &eg; a <filename>quickstart-tutorial/Videos/</"
"filename> subfolder inside the project folder."
msgstr ""
"第一步是为我们的新项目创建一个新的 (空) 文件夹。我会在本教程中称之为 "
"<filename>quickstart-tutorial/</filename> 。 然后获取一些样本视频片段，或从这"
"里下载它们：<ulink url=\"http://granjow.net/uploads/kdenlive/manual/kdenlive-"
"tutorial-videos-2011-avi.tar.bz2\">kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-avi.tar."
"bz2</ulink> (7 MB)<footnote><para>如果您喜欢Theora (您可能不喜欢，因为Ogg "
"Video 通常导致问题)，请先选择Theora,，以下载 <ulink url=\"http://granjow.net/"
"uploads/kdenlive/manual/kdenlive-tutorial-videos-2011-ogv.tar.bz2\">kdenlive-"
"tutorial-videos-2011-ogv.tar.bz2</ulink>。</para></footnote>, 并将它们解压缩"
"到 &eg; 一个 <filename>quickstart-tutorial/Videos/</filename> 项目文件夹内的"
"子文件夹。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The image on the left shows the suggested directory structure: Each project "
"has its own directory, with video files in the <filename>Videos</filename> "
"subdirectory, audio files in the <filename>Audio</filename> directory, &etc; "
"(<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual/"
"Projects_and_Files#File_Structure\">read more</ulink>)"
msgstr ""
"左侧的图像显示了建议的目录结构：每个项目都有自己的目录， 包含 "
"<filename>Videos</filename> 子目录中的视频文件, <filename>Audio</filename> 子"
"目录中的音频文件 &etc; (<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:"
"myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual/Projects_and_Files#File_Structure\">阅读更多</"
"ulink>)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"(The tutorial from now on assumes that you use the sample videos provided, "
"but it works with any.)"
msgstr "(从现在开始的教程假定你使用所提供的样本视频，但是它适用于任何情况。)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New Project dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>新项目对话框</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>New Project dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>新项目对话框</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open &kdenlive; and create a new project (<menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"打开 &kdenlive; 并创建一个新项目 (<menuchoice><guimenu>文件</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>新</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the previously created project folder (<filename>quickstart-tutorial/"
"</filename>) and select an appropriate project profile. The video files "
"provided above are 720p, 23.98 fps.<footnote><para><ulink url=\"http://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/720p\">720</ulink> is the video height, p stands for "
"<ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Progressive_scan\">progressive "
"scan</ulink> in contrast to <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Interlaced_video\">interlaced video</ulink>, and the fps number denotes the "
"number of full frames per second.</para></footnote> If you are using your "
"own files and don’t know which one to use, &kdenlive; will suggest an "
"appropriate one when the first clip is added <footnote><para>Provided "
"Configure Kdenlive Settings under <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/"
"Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual/Settings_Menu/Configure_Kdenlive#Misc"
"\">Misc</ulink> is set to <emphasis>Check if first added clip matches "
"project profile</emphasis></para></footnote> , so you can leave the field on "
"whatever it is."
msgstr ""
"选择先前创建的项目文件夹 (<filename>quickstart-tutorial/</filename>) 并选择一"
"个合适的项目配置文件。 上面提供的录像文件为720p、23.98fps。"
"<footnote><para><ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/720p\">720</ulink> "
"为视频高度， p 表示 <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Progressive_scan\">渐进扫描</ulink> 不同于 <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Interlaced_video\">交错视频</ulink>fps 数字表示每秒的完整帧数。</"
"para></footnote> 如果您正在使用自己的文件，不知道要使用哪个文件 &kdenlive; 在"
"第一个素材被添加时建议一个合适的素材 <footnote><para>提供配置Kdenlive 设置为 "
"<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual/"
"Settings_Menu/Configure_Kdenlive#Misc\">杂项</ulink> 设置为 <emphasis>检查是"
"否首次添加的素材匹配项目配置</emphasis></para></footnote> 这样你就可以离开这"
"个字段，不管它是什么地方。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding clips"
msgstr "添加剪辑"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Project Bin: Adding video clips</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>项目素材库： 添加视频素材</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Project Bin: Adding video clips</para>"
msgstr "<para>项目素材库： 添加视频素材</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that the project is ready, let’s start adding some clips (&ie; the ones "
"you downloaded). This works via the <emphasis>Project Bin widget</emphasis>; "
"a click on the <guilabel>Add Clip</guilabel> icon <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-add-clip.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> directly opens the file dialog, a click on "
"the small arrow shows a list of additional clip types that can be added as "
"well. Video clips, audio clips, images, and other &kdenlive; projects can be "
"added via the default <guilabel>Add Clip</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"现在项目已经准备就绪，让我们开始添加一些片段(&ie; 是你下载的片段)。 通过 "
"<emphasis>项目素材库部件</emphasis>来实现这一点； 点击 <guilabel>添加素材</"
"guilabel> 图标 <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"add-clip.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> 直接打开"
"文件对话框；单击小箭头显示一个也可以添加的额外片段类型列表。 视频剪辑、音频剪"
"辑、图像和其他 &kdenlive; 项目可以通过默认 <guilabel>添加素材</guilabel> 对话"
"框添加。"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Kdenlive window with the tutorial files</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>带有教程文件的 Kdenlive 窗口</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Kdenlive window with the tutorial files</para>"
msgstr "<para>带有教程文件的 Kdenlive 窗口</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After loading the clips, &kdenlive; will look similar to this. On the top "
"left there is the already known project tree. Right of it are the monitors "
"that show video; The clip monitor displays video from the original clips, "
"the project monitor shows how the output video will look, with all effects, "
"transitions, &etc; applied. The third, also very important, item is the "
"timeline (below the monitors): This is the place where the video clips will "
"be edited. There are two different types of tracks, Video and Audio. Video "
"tracks can contain any kind of clip, audio tracks as well – but when "
"dropping a video file to the audio track, only the audio will be used."
msgstr ""
"加载素材后， &kdenlive; 将看起来与此相似。在左上方有已知的项目工程目录。 右侧"
"为显示视频的监视器；素材监视器显示来自原素材的视频， 项目监视器将展示最终输出"
"是什么样的，包含所有效果，过渡， &etc。 非常重要的第三项是时间轴(在监视器下"
"方)：这是编辑视频剪辑的地方。 有两种不同类型的轨道：视频轨道和音频轨道。 视频"
"轨道可以包含任何类型的素材片段，音频轨道也可以 — — 但当将视频文件拖放到音轨"
"时，只会使用音频。"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Saving a Kdenlive project</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>保存 Kdenlive 项目</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Saving a Kdenlive project</para>"
msgstr "<para>保存 Kdenlive 项目</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let’s save the work via <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This saves our project, &ie; "
"where we placed the clips on the timeline, which effects we applied, and so "
"on. It can <emphasis>not</emphasis> be played.<footnote><para>To be correct, "
"it <emphasis>can</emphasis> be played using <varname>melt yourproject."
"kdenlive</varname>, but this is not the way you would want to present your "
"final video since it is (most likely) too slow. Additionally, it only works "
"if melt is installed.</para></footnote> The process of creating the final "
"video is called <emphasis>Rendering</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"让我们通过<menuchoice><guimenu>文件</guimenu><guimenuitem>保存</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>来保存工作。这将保存我们的项目 &ie;素材在时间轴的位"
"置，应用的效果，等等。项目文件<emphasis>不能</emphasis>被播放。"
"<footnote><para>纠正一下，它<emphasis>可</emphasis>通过<varname>melt "
"yourproject.kdenlive</varname>播放，但者并不是你最终想要展示视频的方式，因为"
"这样(渲染)太慢了。此外，只有在melt安装后才可工作。</para></footnote>创建最终"
"视频的过程叫做<emphasis>渲染</emphasis>。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Timeline"
msgstr "时间线"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See also <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/"
"Manual/Timeline\">Timeline section of the manual</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"另请参考 <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/"
"Manual/Timeline\">手册的时间线部分</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now comes the actual editing. Project clips are combined to the final result "
"on the timeline. They get there by drag and drop: Drag some Napoli (assuming "
"you are using the files provided above, as in the rest of this quick start "
"tutorial; If not, please make sure your screen is waterproof, and perhaps "
"tomatoproof) from the project tree, and drop it onto the first track in the "
"timeline."
msgstr ""
"现在实际操作编辑。项目视频将由时间轴上的片段组合而来。它们被拖放到那里：从项"
"目目录中拖动一些 Napoli（假定你正在使用上面提供的文件，与这个快速入门教程的其"
"他部分相同）并将其放到时间轴中的第一条轨道。"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>First clips in the timeline</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>时间轴中的第一个素材</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>First clips in the timeline</para>"
msgstr "<para>时间轴中的第一个素材</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since some cutlery is needed as well, grab the spoon clip and drop it on the "
"first track as well. Then drag the Napoli to the beginning of the timeline "
"(otherwise the rendered video would start with some seconds of plain black), "
"and the Spoon right after the Napoli, such that it looks like in the image "
"on the left. (Where I have zoomed in with <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Wheel</"
"keycap></keycombo>.)"
msgstr ""
"既然也需要一些切片，就抢走点片段并将其拖到第一条轨道。 然后拖动拿破仑到时间线"
"的开头(否则渲染的视频将以黑色几秒钟开始) 以及拿破仑之后的Spoon，让它看起来像"
"在左边的图像中。 (我已用 <keycombo>缩放的地方&Ctrl;<keycap>轮</keycap></"
"keycombo>.)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Timeline cursor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>时间线光标</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Timeline cursor</para>"
msgstr "<para>时间线光标</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result can already be previewed by pressing <keycap>Space</keycap> (or "
"the <guilabel>Play</guilabel> button in the project monitor). You will see "
"the Napoli directly followed by a Spoon. If the timeline cursor is not at "
"the beginning, the project monitor will start playing somewhere in the "
"middle; you can move it by dragging it either on the timeline ruler or in "
"the project monitor. If you prefer keyboard shortcuts, <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo> does the same for the monitor that is "
"activated. (Select the <guilabel>Project Monitor</guilabel> if it is not "
"selected yet before using the shortcut.)"
msgstr ""
"目前已经支持通过按 :kbd:`Space` (或项目监视器中的 :guilabel:`播放` 按钮)来预"
"览结果。 你会看到 Spoon 直接跟在 Napoli 后面。 如果时间轴光标尚未开始，项目监"
"视器将在中间的某个位置开始播放； 您可以通过在时间轴标尺或项目监视器中拖动它来"
"移动它。 如果您喜欢键盘快捷键， :kbd:`Ctrl + Home` 按键可以对被激活的监视器做"
"同样的操作。 (如果在使用快捷键之前尚未选中，请选中 :menuselection:`项目监视器"
"` 。)"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Resize marker</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>调整时间线光标大小</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Resize marker</para>"
msgstr "<para>调整标记大小</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since after eating comes playing, there is a Billiards clip. Add it to the "
"timeline as well. For the first 1.5 seconds nothing happens in the clip, so "
"it should perhaps be <guilabel>cut</guilabel> to avoid the video becoming "
"boring. An easy way<footnote><para>Writing it this way suggests that there "
"are several ways of cutting a clip. This is in fact true.</para></footnote> "
"for this is to move the timeline cursor to the desired position (&ie; the "
"position where you want to cut the video), then drag the left border of the "
"clip when the resize marker appears. It will snap in at the timeline cursor "
"when you move close enough."
msgstr ""
"因为吃完后开始玩耍，所以有一个十亿的片段。同时添加到时间线。对于前一个。 秒片"
"段中不会发生任何事情，所以它也许应该为 <guilabel>剪切</guilabel> 来避免视频变"
"得枯燥无味。 一种简单的方法<footnote><para>这样写它意味着有几种方法来剪切片"
"段。 这实际上是事实。</para></footnote> 这需要将时间线光标移动到所需位置"
"(&ie; 你想要剪切视频的位置)， 然后在缩放标记出现时拖动片段的左边框。 当您移动"
"足够关闭时，它会在时间线光标处吸附。"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Overlapping clips</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>重叠剪辑</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Overlapping clips</para>"
msgstr "<para>重叠剪辑</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a <emphasis>transition</emphasis> between eating (the Spoon) and "
"playing billiards, the two clips need to overlap. To be precise: the second "
"clip should be above or below the first one and end some frames after the "
"second one begins. Zooming in until the ticks for single frames appear helps "
"here; it also makes it easy to always have the same transition duration, "
"five frames in this case."
msgstr ""
"要在进食(Spoon)和玩十亿个玩家之间添加 <emphasis>过渡</emphasis> ，两个片段需"
"要重叠。 确切：第二个片段应该在第一个片段上方或以下，在第二个片段开始后结束一"
"些帧。 放大直到单帧的勾子显示在这里有所帮助； 它还使得总是有相同的过渡期，在"
"这种情况下有5个框架。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can zoom in by either using the <guilabel>zoom slider</guilabel> at the "
"bottom of the &kdenlive; window, or with <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Mousewheel</"
"keycap></keycombo>. &kdenlive; will zoom to the timeline cursor, so first "
"set it to the position which you want to see enlarged, then zoom in."
msgstr ""
"您可以在 &kdenlive; 窗口底部使用 <guilabel>缩放滑块</guilabel> 缩放， 或使用 "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>鼠标</keycap></keycombo> &kdenlive; 将缩放到时间线曲"
"线上，所以首先将其设置为你想要扩大的位置，然后放大。"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Transition marker</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>调整时间线光标大小</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Transition marker</para>"
msgstr "<para>调整时间线光标大小</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that the clips overlap, the transition can be added. This is done either "
"by right-clicking on the upper clip and choosing <guilabel>Add Transition</"
"guilabel> or, easier, by hovering the mouse over the lower right corner of "
"the Spoon clip until the pointing-finger pointer is shown and the message "
"<quote>Click to add transition</quote> appears. The latter, by default, adds "
"a dissolve transition, which is in this case the best idea anyway since the "
"Spoon is not required for playing."
msgstr ""
"既然片段重叠，过渡可以添加。 通过右键点击上层素材并选择 <guilabel>添加离子对"
"</guilabel> 或更简单地这样做。 通过悬停鼠标在Spoon片段右下角直到指针指针被显"
"示和消息 <quote>点击添加连线</quote> 。 默认情况下，后者会增加一个解析过渡，"
"在这种情况下这也是最好的想法，因为Spoon不需要玩游戏。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dissolve transitions fades the first clip into the second one. See also "
"<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual/"
"Transitions\">Transition section of the manual</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"解析离子对将第一个片段淡入第二个片段。另见 <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde."
"org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual/Transitions\">手册过渡部分</ulink>。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let’s now add the last clip, the Piano, and again apply a dissolve "
"transition. When adding it on the first track of the timeline, you need to "
"click on the new clip’s lower left edge to add the transition to the "
"previous clip."
msgstr ""
"现在，让我们添加最后一个片段，也就是钢琴的片段，然后再次应用擦除转换。 当将其"
"添加到时间线的第一轨（轨道 V2）以后，您需要点击新片段左下角来添加过渡到上一个"
"片段。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Effects"
msgstr "特效"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Effect List</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>特效列表</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Effect List</para>"
msgstr "<para>特效列表</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Piano can be colourized by adding an <emphasis>effect</emphasis> to it. "
"Select the piano clip, then double-click the <guilabel>RGB Adjustment</"
"guilabel> effect in the <guilabel>Effect List</guilabel>. If it is not "
"visible, you can get it via <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Effect List</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"钢琴可以通过添加 <emphasis>特效</emphasis> 来颜色化。 选择钢琴片段, 然后双击 "
"<guilabel>RGB 调整</guilabel> 效果在 <guilabel>效果列表</guilabel>中。 如果它"
"不可见, 你可以通过 <menuchoice><guimenu>查看</guimenu> <guimenuitem>效果列表"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the effect has been added, its name will be added to the timeline clip. "
"It will also be shown in the <guilabel>Properties</guilabel> widget."
msgstr ""
"一旦添加特效，它的名称将被添加到时间轴片段。 它也将在 <guilabel>属性</"
"guilabel> 部件中显示。"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Effect Stack with RGB adjustment</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>带有RGB 调整的效果堆栈</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Effect Stack with RGB adjustment</para>"
msgstr "<para>带有RGB 调整的效果堆栈</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get a warm yellow-orange tone on the image, fitting the comfortable "
"evening, blue needs to be reduced and red and green improved."
msgstr ""
"为了将图像的色调改为橙黄色，使其适宜在晚上观看，我们需要减少蓝色，增加红绿"
"色。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The values in the Properties widget can be changed by using the slider "
"(middle mouse button resets it to the default value), or by entering a value "
"directly by double-clicking the number to the right of the slider."
msgstr ""
"效果/合成堆栈中的值可以通过滑块更改（鼠标中键将其重置为默认值），或者直接通过"
"双击滑块右侧的数字来输入一个值。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Properties widget always refers to the timeline clip that is currently "
"selected. Each effect can be temporarily disabled by clicking the eye icon, "
"or all effects for that clip can be disabled using the check box at the top "
"of the Properties widget (the settings are saved though), this is &eg; "
"useful for effects that require a lot of computing power, so they can be "
"disabled when editing and enabled again for rendering."
msgstr ""
"效果/合成堆栈小部件总是对应当前选择的时间轴上的片段。单击特效边上的眼睛图标，"
"可以暂时禁用这个效果；或者点击效果/合成堆栈顶部的复选框，可以暂时禁用该片段的"
"所有效果（但这些效果设置已保存）。这对需要大量算力的效果非常有用，可以在编辑"
"时禁用它们来节约算力，在渲染时再次企业。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For some effects, like the one used there, it is possible to add keyframes. "
"The framed watch icon indicates this. Keyframes are used for changing effect "
"parameters over time. In our clip this allows us to fade the piano’s colour "
"from a warm evening colour to a cold night colour."
msgstr ""
"对于某些效果，例如在这里使用的效果，我们可以添加关键帧。帧上的手表图标表明了"
"这一点：关键帧用于随着时间的推移更改效果参数。 在我们的素材中，这使我们能够将"
"钢琴的颜色从晚上的暖色自然渐变到深夜的冷色。"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Keyframes for effects</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>效果的关键帧</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Keyframes for effects</para>"
msgstr "<para>效果的关键帧</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After clicking the <guilabel>keyframe</guilabel> icon (the clock icon framed "
"in the previous image), the Properties widget will re-arrange. By default "
"there will be two keyframes, one at the beginning of the timeline clip and "
"one at the end. Move the timeline cursor to the end of the timeline clip, "
"such that the project monitor actually shows the new colours when changing "
"the parameters of the keyframe at the end."
msgstr ""
"点击 <guilabel>关键帧</guilabel> 图标 (前一图像中的时钟图标)，属性部件将重新"
"排序。 默认情况下，将有两个关键框架，一个在时间线片段的开头，另一个在结尾。 "
"将时间线光标移动到时间线片段末尾， 这样项目监视器在更改关键帧的参数时实际显示"
"新的颜色。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure the last keyframe is selected in the Properties list. Then you are "
"ready to flood the piano with a deep blue."
msgstr "请确保最后一个关键帧在属性列表中被选中。然后您准备用深蓝水淹没钢琴。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moving the timeline cursor to the beginning of the project and playing it "
"(with <keycap>Space</keycap>, or the <guilabel>Play</guilabel> button in the "
"<guilabel>Project Monitor</guilabel>), the piano should now change the "
"colour as desired."
msgstr ""
"将时间线光标移动到项目开始并播放(使用 <keycap>空格</keycap>) 或 <guilabel>播"
"放</guilabel> 按钮在 <guilabel>项目监视器</guilabel>中, 钢琴现在应该按照需要"
"更改颜色。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keyframing was the hardest part of this tutorial. If you managed to do it, "
"you will master &kdenlive; easily!"
msgstr ""
"密钥框架是本教程中最困难的部分。如果你设法这样做，你会轻松掌握 &kdenlive;！"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See also <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/"
"Manual/Effects\">Effects section of the manual</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"同时查看 <ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/"
"Manual/Effects\">手册效果部分</ulink>。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Music"
msgstr "音乐"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Audio fadeout</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>音频淡出</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Audio fadeout</para>"
msgstr "<para>音频淡出</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since the clips do not provide any audio, let’s search for some nice piece "
"of music, from your local collection or on web pages like <ulink url="
"\"http://www.jamendo.com\">Jamendo</ulink>. The audio clip should, after "
"adding it, be dragged to an audio track on the timeline."
msgstr ""
"因为片段没有提供任何音频，让我们搜索一些精彩的音乐， 来自您的本地收藏或网页上"
"的 <ulink url=\"http://www.jamendo.com\">Jamendo</ulink>。 音频素材添加后应拖"
"动到时间线上的音轨上。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The audio clip can be resized on the timeline the same way as video clips "
"are. The cursor will snap in at the end of the project automatically. To add "
"a fade out effect at the end of the audio clip (except if you found a file "
"with exactly the right length) you can hover the top right (or left) edge of "
"the timeline clip and drag the red shaded triangle to the position where "
"fading out should start."
msgstr ""
"音频素材可以像视频片段一样按时间轴调整大小。 光标将在项目结束时自动吸附。 要"
"在音频片段末尾添加淡出效果(除非您找到的文件准确正确长度)，您可以将时间线片段"
"的右上角(或左边)悬停，并将红色阴影三角形拖到应开始淡出的位置。"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This shaded triangle is a shorthand for adding the effect "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Fade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Fade out</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Both ways lead to the same result."
msgstr ""
"这个阴影三角形是添加特效 <menuchoice><guimenu>淡出</guimenu> <guimenuitem>淡"
"出</guimenuitem></menuchoice>的缩写。 这两种方法都导致了同样的结果。"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rendering"
msgstr "渲染（导出）"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Rendering dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>渲染对话框</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Rendering dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>渲染对话框</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A few minutes left, and the project is finished! Click the Render button (or "
"go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Project</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Render</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or press <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo>) to "
"get the dialog shown on the left. Select the desired output file for our new "
"video with all effects and transitions, choose MP4 (works nearly "
"everywhere), select the output file location and press the <guilabel>Render "
"to File</guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"剩下几分钟，项目已完成！ 点击渲染按钮(或转到 <menuchoice><guimenu>项目</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>渲染</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, 或按 <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"&Enter;</keycombo>) 获取左侧显示的对话框。 为我们的新视频选择所需的输出文件，"
"具有全部效果和过渡效果，选择 MP4 (几乎所有地方都能使用)， 选择输出文件位置并"
"按 <guilabel>渲染到文件</guilabel> 按钮。"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Rendering progress</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>渲染进度</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Rendering progress</para>"
msgstr "<para>渲染进度</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After some seconds rendering will be finished, and your first &kdenlive; "
"project completed. Congratulations!"
msgstr "几秒钟后渲染将完成，您的第一个 &kdenlive; 项目将完成。恭喜！"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "Complete manual"
msgstr "完整手册"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Further documentation for the current version of &kdenlive; can be found in "
"<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde.org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual"
"\">the full manual</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"有关&kdenlive;；当前版本的更多文档；可以在<ulink url=\"http://userbase.kde."
"org/Special:myLanguage/Kdenlive/Manual\">查看完整手册。"

